summary: Computing 2D softmax activation for random input tensor of shape (2,3).

details.comment: Computing 2D softmax activation for random input tensor of shape (2,3).
details.content:
import torch
import torch.nn as nn
m = nn.Softmax(dim=1)
input = torch.randn(2, 3, requires_grad=True)
output = m(input)
print(output)
